title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Bryant Gumble here, with Mary Nissenson, who is in her second week while Jane Pauley is on maternity leave.” [From NBC Today, 8 a.m., January 9, 1984. Submitted by Robert J. Powers, Shreveport, Louisiana.]
